<main class="container">
    <section class="card">
        <h2>Precautions for Return or Exchange</h2>
        <p><b>All return or exchange requests must undergo a quality check. The following reasons for return or exchange may not be accepted:</b></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Damage caused by the customer</li>
            <li>A significant decrease in the product's value due to customer use or consumption.</li>
            <li>Minor scratches, dents, spots, or discoloration resulting from manufacturing defects. The album's plastic cover and outer box are designed to protect the actual contents.
            <li>Only items with severe damage, defects, or missing parts caused by the courier or manufacturer will be considered for return or exchange.</li>
            
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
        <h2>Return or Exchange Procedure</h2>
        <div class="info-group">
            <p> <b> 1. </b>Contact Customer Service (CS) to request a return or exchange. </p>
            <p> <b> 2. </b>Provide a video showing the unboxing of the parcel and highlighting the defect of the item you wish to return.</p>
            <p> <b> 3. </b>A CS representative will investigate the issue to determine if a return or exchange is possible and will arrange for the item to be picked up. </p>
            <p> <b> 4. </b>Once we receive the returned item, it will be quality-checked, and we will initiate an exchange or refund as appropriate. </p>
        </ul>
    </section>
        

    <section class="card">
        <h2>Return and Exchange Fees</h2>
        <p>All return and exchange fees will be covered by us. However, if there is evidence of malicious intent regarding the return, the item may not be exchanged, and no refund or exchange will be issued.</p>
        
    </section>

   
    
